Package: issb
Type: Package
Title: R code associated with the book chapter "Simulation of stochastic
    kinetic models"
Version: 0.1
Date: 2012-07-17
Author: Colin Gillespie
Maintainer: Colin Gillespie <colin.gillespie@newcastle.ac.uk>
Description: R code associated with the book chapter "Simulation of stochastic
    kinetic models", published in "In silico Systems Biology: A systems-based
    approach to understanding biological processes"" by Humana Press. This
    package provides a simple interface to simulating tochastic kinetic models.
Depends:
    deSolve,
    MASS,
    parallel
License: GPL
Collate:
    'create_model.R'
    'deterministic.R'
    'diffusion.R'
    'gillespie.R'
    'lna.R'
    'pleap.R'
    'discretise.R'
    'multiple_sim.R'
